Error: accumulator width mismatch calling 'app_init': caller is 8-bit, callee expects 16-bit
   ╭─[ tests/golden/fixtures/link-multi-func-err/input.10-main.k65:7:10 ]
   │
 7 │     call app_init
   │          ────┬───  
   │              ╰───── caller A=8-bit, callee 'app_init' expects A=16-bit
   │ 
   │ Help: switch the accumulator to @a16 (matching 'app_init's declared width) before this call, or change the callee's `@a8`/`@a16` annotation if it should be the other width
   │ 
   │ Note: The W65C816's `m` flag picks 8- vs 16-bit accumulator opcodes; the linker reads each function's declared `@a8`/`@a16` and rejects calls where the caller's runtime mode would silently encode against the wrong width.
───╯

Error: index register width mismatch calling 'app_init': caller is 8-bit, callee expects 16-bit
   ╭─[ tests/golden/fixtures/link-multi-func-err/input.10-main.k65:7:10 ]
